<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Friedrich IV. und Wilhelm II., Markgrafen von Meißen</head><p>Der Rat bittet für Peter Fürer, Bürger zu Nürnberg, um Unterstützung wegen Bezahlung von Schulden mehrerer Bürger und kündigt ihn an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_102" id="49v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_102_r1l1"><expan>Frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> vnd <expan>wılh<ex>elm</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_102_r1l2">Margrafen cʒu Meihſen</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_102_r1l3"><expan>Gnedıge<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> vns hat fürgelegt Peter Fürer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_102_r1l4"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> / vvie daʒ Jm ~ etlıche dıe <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> etwieuil ſchuldig </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_102_r1l5">ſein vnd <expan>gelte<ex>n</ex></expan> ſüllen daʒ Jm von Jn niht becʒalt künn vverd<gap reason="illegible"/></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_102_r1l6">vnd Jm das alſo mit gevvalte <expan>vorhalte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒıeh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / als </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_102_r1l7">Er das <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> ſelber auch müntlıch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_102_r1l8">
<del rend="strikethrough">ſel </del> wol <expan>fürgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>ercʒele<ex>n</ex></expan> wirdt / <expan>Bıt<ex>en</ex></expan> vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_102_r1l10"> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> fleiſʒ / daʒ Jr 
<add><ab facs="#facs_102_r1l9"><expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>vvıllıg<ex>en</ex></expan> dınſt <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> mit ~ den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_102_r1l11"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> ſchicken vnd <expan>beſtelle<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet / daʒ <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_102_r1l13"><expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> dieſelbe ſein ſchulde 
<add><ab facs="#facs_102_r1l12">noch on <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒıehen</expan> </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> von de </del> gerıht vnd becʒalt werde </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_102_r1l14">oder Darümb ein <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒog<ex>en</ex></expan> ſlewnig reht wıderuare </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_102_r1l15">Als etc / das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_102" id="49v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> und <expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan>,
                        margrafen czu Meihsen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab><expan>Gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, uns hat fürgelegt Peter Fürer,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie daz im etliche die
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> etwievil schuldig sein und
                                <expan>gelte<ex>n</ex></expan> süllen, daz im von in niht beczalt
                        künn werd<app>
<note><gap reason="illegible"/></note>
</app> und im das also mit gewalte <expan>vorhalte<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>czieh<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, als er das
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> selber auch müntlich wol
                                <expan>fürgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                            <expan>erczele<ex>n</ex></expan> wirdt. <expan>Bit<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        fleisz, daz ir <add><expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>willig<ex>en</ex></expan> dinst
                            <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan></add> von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> mit den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> schicken
                        und <expan>bestelle<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet, daz
                            <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, dieselbe sein schulde <add>noch on
                                    <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cziehen</expan></add> geriht und beczalt
                        werde oder darümb ein <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czog<ex>en</ex></expan> slewnig
                        reht widervare, als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. </ab></div>
</div></body>
